A toolkit for loading and rendering a 3d world.

Dependencies:
Unofficial OpenGL Software Development Kit: http://glsdk.sourceforge.net/ - Only glm, glload, glutil and glimg
Open Asset Import Library: http://assimp.sourceforge.net/ (without boost)
SDL with SDL_image

The glsdk doesn't have a make install command, specify path to it in the Makefile (GLSDK_PATH)
